            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <input
          maxlength="12"
          name="field_whatsapp"
          size="20"
          type="text"
          class="block w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-2.5 pl-10 text-sm text-gray-900 focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500"
          placeholder="Numero Whatsapp"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="field_pregunta1" class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium"
          >¿Por qué quieres ser parte de Incrementa Tu Consulta?
        </label>
        <input
          maxlength="100"
          class="block w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-2.5 pl-10 text-sm text-gray-900 focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500"
          name="field_pregunta1"
          size="20"
          type="text"
          placeholder=""
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="field_pregunta2" class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium"
          >¿Estarías dispuesto a invertir en ti mismo, ya que es un programa que
          tiene un valor por encima de $1,000 dólares?
        </label>
        <input
          maxlength="100"
          class="block w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-2.5 pl-10 text-sm text-gray-900 focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500"
          name="field_pregunta2"
          size="20"
          type="text"
          placeholder=""
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="webform-lists" style="display: none;">
      <div style="display:flex;" class="checkboxes js-[11] Grupo Vip">
        <label class="container-box">
          <input
            type="checkbox"
            name="publiclistid"
            id="QPtDUmAS"
            value="744c2c13-5b13-4ca0-aeb3-e054c20972f3"
            checked="checked"
          />
        </label>
        <label class="publiclistlabel" for="QPtDUmAS">[11] Grupo Vip</label>
      </div>
    </div>
  </fieldset>
  <fieldset class="webform-options style-updated" style="border:none;">
    <input
      type="submit"
      name="submit"
      value="¡ Quiero ser VIP !"
      id="eesubmit"
      class={`mt-8 w-full rounded-lg bg-green-600 px-8 py-4 font-coolvetica text-2xl font-black text-white hover:bg-green-500 md:text-4xl`}
    />
    <input
      type="hidden"
      name="publicaccountid"
      value="9377d1ed-c310-4467-b52c-bee4e5379dcb"
    />
    <input
      type="hidden"
      name="returnUrl"
      value="https://www.incrementatuconsulta.com/graciasvip/"
    />
    <input
      type="hidden"
      name="activationReturnUrl"
      value="https://www.incrementatuconsulta.com/graciasvip/"
    />
    <input
      type="hidden"
      name="alreadyactiveurl"
      value="https://www.incrementatuconsulta.com/graciasvip/"
    />
    <input type="hidden" name="activationTemplate" value="" />
    <input type="hidden" name="source" value="WebForm" />
    <input
      type="hidden"
      name="verifyemail"
      value="false"
      id="ewf_verifyEmails"
    />
    <input type="hidden" id="ewf_captcha" name="captcha" value="false" />
    <input type="hidden" name="sendActivation" value="true" />
    <input type="hidden" name="notifyEmail" value="" />
    <button
      type="button"
      name="dismissForm"
      id="ewf_dismissForm"
      style="display:none; position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; float: right"
      >X
    </button>
  </fieldset>
</form>
